<http://www.spektrix.com/improvcentrevancouver/event/45401AJDKTHQLVSLBBVQGBPQSVNVKLQMM>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "LGBTQIA2S+ Intro to Improv";
  schema:description """
	<h2>Free LGBTQIA2S+ Workshop!</h2><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Time:</span> 3:30pm – 5:30pm<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Ages:</span> 19+<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Level Required:</span> no improv experience is required!<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Workshop Capacity:</span> 22 people<span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Cost:</span> FREE with registration<span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Max 1 enrollment per email</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Looking to explore the world of improvisation? Join us for an engaging workshop for LGBTQIA2S+ participants, regardless of prior experience! Dive into the fundamentals of improv during this two-hour session designed specifically for beginners. Experience the joy of \"Yes, And!\" in a welcoming and supportive atmosphere.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>All workshops and classes are 19+ only.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>LOCK OUT POLICY: Doors will lock 15 minutes after the class begins. Late comers will not be permitted.<span><br/></span>
""";
