<http://www.spektrix.com/improvcentrevancouver/event/59401AVPBDGTDRSCSDKLHRHSTPMLPGGSV>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Theatresports Unhinged!";
  schema:description """
	<h2>Fridays & Saturdays at 9:30pm</h2><span><br/></span>Come join us for a twisted take on the classic format! See the unexpected become the norm, and the forbidden become fair game! If you’re a fan of our regular Theatresports™ shows, get ready to have your funny bones broken with Theatresports™ Unhinged!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Rating: 🌶️🌶️🌶️🌶️ – Shows may include adult themes and swearing with more explicit references to sexual or violent themes. Best for older teens and adults. (18A)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Please Note: as The Improv Centre is a licensed facility, all minors (persons under the age of 19) must be accompanied by an adult.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>All physical vouchers must now be redeemed via phone or email. Please contact the box office for assistance.
""";
