<http://www.spektrix.com/improvcentrevancouver/event/61201ARKNPQJBTCNRNPMQMMBCRPGCCDLM>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "TIC Summer Games";
  schema:description """
	<h1>Break up your summer day with a side-splitting improv matinee!</h1><span><br/></span>This summer we’re hosting the TIC Summer Games – where two teams of improvisers compete in a series of high-energy improv challenges that the whole family will love. And after 90-minutes of laughing in some cool A/C, you’ll be ready to head back out for some fun in the sun!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Whether you’re visiting Granville Island for the first time or a local looking to add some improv chaos to your weekend, you’ll have a blast at TIC Summer Games!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Run time: 90 minutes with one 15 minute intermission.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Rated: 🌶️ – Suitable for all audiences. Children are encouraged to attend with a caregiver. (G)<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Please Note: as The Improv Centre is a licensed facility, all minors (persons under the age of 19) must be accompanied by an adult.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>All physical vouchers must now be redeemed via phone or email. Please contact the box office for assistance.
""";
  schema:startDate "2026-07-11T14:00:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
  schema:image <https://system.spektrix.com/improvcentrevancouver/files/c9d4391f-bbef-4735-95da-368f33bd2591.jpg>;
